-10-27-%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%8D%80%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E5%93%A1-%E8%B8%A2%E4%BF%9D-%E5%BE%8C%E5%86%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%AD%89-3-%E7%BD%AA-%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E8%87%B3-10-%E6%9C%88%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%8A/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去年 10 月 27 日，網民於尖沙咀發起「追究警暴」集會，最終演變成九龍區多處警民衝突。32 歲電腦技術員被指在長沙灣政府合署外攜有汽油彈，去年 12 月「踢保」後，昨天再度被捕。被告被控暴動、使用蒙面物品等 3 罪，今（25 日）在西九龍裁判法院提堂。裁判官拒絕被告保釋，押至 10 月 6 日再訊，期間還押懲教看管。"},{"pid":"f46ff79e81057e3a64c80c8846b8a3a9bb493b7d","tid":2173523,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:03:47.000Z","msg":"黑警+狗官+太監=港共曱甴集團"},{"pid":"19c383adc512a928ec0071b0a531fe8fa095951b","tid":2173523,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:04:14.000Z","msg":"邊撚個狗官?"},{"pid":"633dd7907e66e5bf6bb7f4bb6caf546e8e29ac65","tid":2173523,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:05:51.000Z","msg":"搞清楚乜野叫踢保未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n踢保唔代表無事, 佢有喜歡一樣照樣拉人"},{"pid":"9763b2df08f747bd06e35c47fc698fcb4ac80fb2","tid":2173523,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"633dd7907e66e5bf6bb7f4bb6caf546e8e29ac65","tid":2173523,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:05:51.000Z","msg":"搞清楚乜野叫踢保未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n踢保唔代表無事, 佢有喜歡一樣照樣拉人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:16:05.000Z","msg":"依家要即時還押但之前又畀保釋係咪有原則性衝突？"},{"pid":"583bc27dd08797204a0adb3c34821a5822f4f4fb","tid":2173523,"uid":3860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"633dd7907e66e5bf6bb7f4bb6caf546e8e29ac65","tid":2173523,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:05:51.000Z","msg":"搞清楚乜野叫踢保未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n踢保唔代表無事, 佢有喜歡一樣照樣拉人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img